$ Avaloq table sec_user
@ sec_user

`sec_user` contains a record for each → Companies-Products/Avaloq/users[user] in an Avaloq environment.

`sec_user` is protected with → development/databases/Oracle/objects/triggers[triggers] against being modified with → development/databases/Oracle/SQL/DML[DML].
The package → Companies-Products/Avaloq/development/plsql-packages/migr_user[`migr_user#`] should be used instead.



gh|about-Avaloq|/tables/sec/user/select.sql||

